   CLINTON-YEAR _ WASHINGTON _ For Bill Clinton, 1998 has been a
roller-coaster ride: from the mire of Monicagate, through months of
ignominous denial culminating in an impeachment vote, and on to
finish as the banner carrier for a party that has clearly seized
the initiative on the strength of his efforts. (Deans, Cox News
Service).
