<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-12-25 17:46 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A6623 &Cx1f; taf-z
s l &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-FASHION-INTELLECTUAL-     12-25 1215
